===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
Chen Jian suggests that the graph derives from {{zh-l|⿱口⿰止止}}, an ideogram shared by {{zh-l|*範}} and {{zh-l|*圍}}: one {{zh-l|*止}} was omitted, and one stroke was slanted to avoid confusion with {{zh-l|*正}}.<ref>陳劍（2020）。「尋『詞』推『字』」之一例：試說殷墟甲骨文中「犯」「圍」兩讀之字。中國文字，(總第四)，71-115。https://www.airitilibrary.com/Article/Detail?DocID=P20241129001-N202501150005-00005
</ref>

